{"tid":1755770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱睇bob叔最新條live片都好強調唔好再聽班白票撚人講中伏","createTime":"2019-11-25T18:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T18:52:29.000Z","uid":38795,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f93bba4ab4166847acf2c58083be453d96261def","tid":1755770,"uid":38795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:01:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4ZXsHHLmgu4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4ZXsHHLmgu4&d=yZvzIFdj7oCTZXRWgogUmZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=dc90af81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4ZXsHHLmgu4</a><br />\n24:36<br />\nbob叔都忍唔著叫人唔好再信白票攬炒論，仲信既仲唔係弱智？<br />\n<br />\n今次大家都知道原來大家團結出盡力投票係會有意想不到既結果，香港民智終於正式開啟<br />\n如果大家仲好似2011 2012 2015 2016咁聽選舉前兩日蒲頭既白票廢票攬炒型五毛講，今日可能就係見到柒婆意氣風發走出黎講區選反映絕大多數市民支持政府止暴制亂，而唔係反思<br />\n<br />\n所以請大家下年立法會同以後都要keep著好似今次咁，唔好俾攬炒型五毛影響，盡力投票打嬴土共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0edddd88d7ab2484419c9ae7c52dd116f3947bf2","tid":1755770,"uid":36808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:02:42.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻一阻大家時間<br />\n<br />\n希望手足可以幫下家長車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無言感激<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747239\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747239</a>"},{"pid":"98c9caf9c8a7f9751ed23f18a5b13325a6631a2b","tid":1755770,"uid":202889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:06:13.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d9c04f5864ec98225b5f92a15754f9b088f7f8","tid":1755770,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:07:19.000Z","msg":"這是事實"},{"pid":"be5ed415606933057f3682fbcf75ba97e9bfd3b8","tid":1755770,"uid